 it!  tank classes are always gonna get more/better hp/ac/haste items and will continue to WIDEN their lead on us in the dmg output department.  in order for verant to &quot;balance&quot; us now, they would have to double our dmg output, give us the ability to attain 5k hps/1k ac and give us no charge items that do healing/cast spells just to make us EVEN with tanks now!  BAH!  this is why I retired my wizzie 4 months ago, I am just now playing it again and am realizing once again that they still haven't figured this out (now there's even more uber tank items, YAY!).  It's common knowledge that verant has a boner for &quot;forgetting&quot; to add new items/abilities to wizards...  They, themselves, seriously have not played the class and don't have a clue what a wizard can/can't do, all they know is we got this big spell that does 1615 dmg and that sounds like too much for them, because they got warriors that can only triple hit for 200 or so every .00001 seconds with haste and that isn't as big as 1615 to them for some reason...not to mention the INSANE dmg they can do with disciplines!  I've seen some do 1k dmg/hit before with disc/rage going on...no way to compete with that at all!  I've been lvl 60 for 8 months, I felt cheated before...now I feel even more cheated...these new spells are just a way to say, &quot;you get to do 2k dmg, then DIE, thx!&quot;  it's a shame I can land a wimpy lure on a mob that does 825 dmg and out-agro ALL the tanks that have already done 2k dmg!  SOMEONE PLEASE GET A CLUE!!!  I'm not even gonna address the fact that after we put out our dmg, we are OOM and have to sit a good 10 minutes (even with clarity/c2)!  sheesh!  tanks get a cheal and keep right on going... /sigh  /wave wizzy<br>
